I agree that employees who are out on leave at PRC time should be encouraged to select reviewers, obtain feedback, and participate in PEP.  Michelle is right, they can do the process from the internet, and in event that they don't have internet access but have email access, we can send the forms to them electronically and manually input their data when the form is returned to us.   

